itunes:summary:
Derek Weida is joined by Owen for another Savage Saturday to discuss what the true meaning of motivation is and how it can be applied to a daily workout regimen, how to make the best use of time during the quarantine, and Derek points out the importance of accepting your downfalls and not letting those ruin your progress in fitness.
